title: Celebrating 7000+ Members!
details: We are excited to announce that our group has reached a remarkable milestone of 7000+ members! Thank you all for being with Green University Computer Club.

title: Invitation for Joining the Discussion Session on Victory Day 2023
details: Join us for an insightful discussion session on Victory Day 2023, hosted by the Computer Science and Engineering (CSE) club. Spearheaded by Jimmy Dane, this event promises engaging conversations and reflections. Marked by his expertise and passion, Jimmy invites you to delve into the significance of Victory Day. The session, scheduled for 16 december, guarantees a thought-provoking exchange of ideas. Don't miss this opportunity to contribute to the discourse on historical triumphs.

title: Executive Committee Meeting
details: Green University Computer Club (GUCC) Executive Committee Meeting Date: 14 December 2023 (Thursday) Venue: 5th floor, Admin Building, Green University of Bangladesh Campus.

title: 5th International Conference
details: The kick off of the 2023 5th International Conference on Sustainable Technologies for Industry 5.0!

title: Internship Opportunity at GCiA
details: Green University Center for International Affairs (GCiA) is looking for Interns. Don't miss out on the opportunity! Scan the given QR Code to apply for the position!

title: EEE Green Poster Hackathon - Season 01
details: Get ready for a burst of creativity at EEE - Green University's -'EEE Green Poster Hackathon - Season 01' this Friday! Let your scientific ideas shine through vibrant posters. Express yourself, leave an impression!

title: EEE Green Poster Hackathon - Season 01
details: Department of Textile Engineering of Green University of Bangladesh conducted an Industrial visit at Horizon Group (5, B.K. Bari, Rajendrapur) on February 15, 2020.
